	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete</strong> button, a confirmation pop-up message will appear before the company is deleted. Click on the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete or <strong>Cancel</strong> button to cancel.</td>
